<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It&apos;s his story, and it&apos;s good. But if you already are convinced of the value of meditation, there are more complete guides out there. Harris even sugg<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It's his story, and it's good. But if you already are convinced of the value of meditation, there are more complete guides out there. Harris even suggests a few at the end of the book along with his own short guide. Try Dr. Mark Epstein and Joseph Goldstein.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
