        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer888264674" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer318852627879093643">I fucking loved this book. It&apos;s the most compelling introduction to meditation I&apos;ve seen, after spending hundreds of dollars buying books on the subject. I have a therapy practice that is mindfulness-based. I often recommend informative-but-boring mindfulness-related books to people that they don&apos;t often finish. They&apos;ll almost certainly finish this one. It&apos;s terrific.</span>
  <span id="freeText318852627879093643" style="display:none">I fucking loved this book. It's the most compelling introduction to meditation I've seen, after spending hundreds of dollars buying books on the subject. I have a therapy practice that is mindfulness-based. I often recommend informative-but-boring mindfulness-related books to people that they don't often finish. They'll almost certainly finish this one. It's terrific.</span>
